dct_title_s: Middle East briefing map : series 1308 / Army Map Service.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Map shows armistice demarcation line, oil pipelines, pumping stations, 2 classes of roads, railroads, and air fields. Stock no. 1308XMEBRMAP. "7-67."
